videos.description: Josh Adams manages to keep his feet for Notre Dame and run for 65-yards to the red zone.
videos.headline: ND's Adams keeps his balance for 65 yards

videos.description: Brandon Wimbush scores a two-yard rushing touchdown after the long running play to give them the lead.
videos.headline: ND's Wimbush takes its himself for the TD

videos.description: Charlie Callinan goes up for a 22-yard touchdown catch from Anthony Brown to give BC the lead.
videos.headline: BC's Callinan leaps for a TD catch

videos.description: Josh Adams breaks out up the middle for 64-yards to take the Irish into the redzone.
videos.headline: Adams gets a big 64-yard run for Notre Dame

videos.description: Brandon Wimbush gets a second rushing touchdown for Notre Dame to take the lead just before halftime.
videos.headline: Wimbush takes the QB sneak for the ND TD

videos.description: Notre Dame Head Coach trusts his young quarterback but wants to lean on the running game for the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Brian Kelly: We have to rely on our running game

videos.description: Notre Dame's Josh Adams gets tripped on a big run but stays up and goes for 36-yards into BC territory.
videos.headline: Josh Adams stays on his feet for 36 yards

videos.description: Brandon Wimbush takes a broken play on 3rd down and turns it into a 65-yard touchdown for Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Wimbush runs 65 yards for his 4th rushing TD

videos.description: Anthony Brown throws a 14-yard touchdown to Charlie Callinan in the corner and is confirmed after review.
videos.headline: Callinan makes another great TD grab for BC

videos.description: Brandon Wimbush spins to lose a defender and steps out just before the end zone just missing out on his 5th rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Wimbush spins and almost scores on 33-yard run

videos.description: Dexter Williams runs up the middle for an easy 15-yard touchdown extending the lead for Notre Dame 49-20.
videos.headline: Williams takes it 15 yards for his 2nd TD

videos.description: Notre Dame QB Brandon Wimbush rushes for 207 yards and four touchdowns as Notre Dame runs over Boston College 49-20.
